//Instructions page This is a simple trivia app \n\n
Regular Mode\n You will be given a number of questions and will be required to answer them. You can adjust the Difficulty of the questions and the number of questions you are asked! \n\n
Timed Mode\n You will be given 10 seconds to answer a question, of random difficulty. If you answer it correctly you will get another question, else your game is over\n\n
High Scores*ONLY IN TIMED MODE*\n If you set a high score you can record it forever imprint your legacy on the leaderboard!
